And I believe we can go
to BBC Scotland

236
00:14:57,440 --> 00:15:00,478
and rejoin Mario Abdullah-Levy,

237
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,989
who is now talking with Ros Lamb.

238
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,838
Ros, that was a terrific run,

239
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:08,430
London to Aberdeen in four and a
half minutes, a new world record.

240
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:10,278
(Squeaky voice) Thanks, yeah.

241
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,720
What happened to your forehead?

242
