with one of her sisters as well.

347
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:14,519
(Pealy) Not at the same time I hope!

348
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,119
(Peter) Here she is!

349
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:20,677
That's four minutes
and fifteen seconds.

350
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,916
That smashes her previous record,

351
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:27,716
by, I think, thirteen seconds,
so that's another world record.

352
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:29,399
- Erm, well done!
- Wow!

353
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:31,477
- Congratulations!
- Two in one show.

354
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:33,637
Well, let's go and say hello.

355
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:42,078
Ros, a new world record -
how do you feel?

356
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:44,316
(Panting)

357
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:47,273
(Peter) As you can see,
the run has really taken its toll,

358
00:22:47,320 --> 00:22:50,074
